I'd love to figure out a better reason for this to be contained, but I don't want to just randomly up the danger at the expense of plausibility. I'm also trying to figure out a way for these things to be less fast-spreading, since if they're too widespread the Foundation would have even less reason to try and contain them (why try to contain the common cold at this point?). My goal is somewhere around SCP-366 for the "mostly contained, but you might still be infected" vibe. Again, I'm eagerly open to suggestions.

Many thanks to Yoric for the pic - I was kinda hoping someone would find something suitable.





